_json.gridTitle: 8 of the Prettiest Old Houses Currently on the Market
_json.description: Listed on the National Register of Historic Places, the Italianate-style David A. Barnes House is situated on over eight acres in the historical river town of Murfreesboro. Behind the house are a number of charming outbuildings that are original to the property. We only wish the dog were part of the package. For more information and photos, visit Preservation North Carolina. Asking Price: $475,000 Listing Agent: Elicia Revelle, United Country Joe Murray Realty; (252) 396-1244   - CountryLiving.com
